csvWfAssignedActivityTemplateBegin.csvdescription: The task exists to allow the Authorrole to be set by this workflow# without this task the roles are not assignable. This is because the workflow is analysed to determine the roles which are required for the tasks within the workflow and the Author performed tasks are in other individualized workflows.

csvWfAssignedActivityTemplateBegin.csvinstructions: This task will rework the data module.@Please give a rework comment to the author by typing in to the rework commend box below.

csvWfExpression.csvexprBody: wt.workflow.engine.WfActivity activity = (wt.workflow.engine.WfActivity) self.getObject();@@// If the reworkComment is not valid# throw an exception@if (reworkComments.trim().length() == 0) {@ throw new wt.workflow.engine.FailedTransitionException (com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.s1000D.S1000DMessages.class.getName()# com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.s1000D.S1000DMessages.BLANK_REWORK_COMMENT# null); @}@@// Set the rework comments for the author@com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.log(org.apache.log4j.Level.DEBUG# activity# "Comments set in reworkComments Variable.");@

csvWfAssignedActivityTemplateBegin.csvdescription: Allows the Logistics Prime to assign group/participants to Validator role required to review the Document.
csvWfAssignedActivityTemplateBegin.csvinstructions: This is an optional task. You do not need to complete this immediately.@@Please set the Validator(s) that will be reviewing the data module.

csvWfExpression.csvexprBody: wt.workflow.engine.WfActivity activity = (wt.workflow.engine.WfActivity) self.getObject();@@// Ensure all the roles have been assigned a participant@if (!com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.checkGivenRoleIsFilled(activity#wt.project.Role.toRole("VALIDATOR"))) {@ wt.util.WTMessage message = new wt.util.WTMessage(com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowActionsRB.class.getName()# com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowActionsRB.EMPTY_ROLES# null);@ throw new wt.util.WTException(message);@} else {@ com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.log(org.apache.log4j.Level.DEBUG# activity# "Validator has been set");@}

csvWfAssignedActivityTemplateBegin.csvdescription: This task allows an individual to claim the work for the Validator role. By completing this task# only this user is kept for the Validator role for this DM. All other Validator individuals are removed from the role for this DM.

csvWfExpression.csvexprBody: wt.workflow.engine.WfProcess process = ((wt.workflow.engine.WfActivity) self.getObject()).getParentProcess();@wt.epm.EPMDocument document = (wt.epm.EPMDocument)primaryBusinessObject;@@//Assign the current user to the Logistics Prime role@wt.project.Role validatorRole = wt.project.Role.toRole("VALIDATOR");@wt.org.WTPrincipal currentUser=wt.session.SessionMgr.getPrincipal();@@wt.team.Team localTeam = wt.team.TeamHelper.service.getTeam(document);@@if(localTeam == null){@System.out.println("Team does not exist");@throw new wt.util.WTException("Team Does Not Exist");@}@java.util.Vector roles = localTeam.getRoles();@java.util.Enumeration e = roles.elements();@while(e.hasMoreElements()){@wt.project.Role role = (wt.project.Role)e.nextElement();@if(role.toString().equalsIgnoreCase("VALIDATOR")){@//Remove all other principals@java.util.Enumeration e2 = localTeam.getPrincipalTarget(role);@while(e2.hasMoreElements()){@wt.org.WTPrincipalReference principal = (wt.org.WTPrincipalReference)e2.nextElement();@if(principal.getPrincipal() != currentUser){@wt.team.TeamHelper.service.deleteRolePrincipalMap(wt.project.Role.toRole("VALIDATOR")# principal.getPrincipal()# (wt.team.WTRoleHolder2) localTeam);@}@}@//Now set the current user as the Illustrator@wt.team.TeamHelper.service.addRolePrincipalMap(wt.project.Role.toRole("VALIDATOR")# currentUser# (wt.team.WTRoleHolder2) localTeam);@}@}

csvWfExprRobotTemplateBegin.csvdescription: This node will initialize the workflow variables# Synchronize and Validate the document# refresh the workspaces# and set the previous roles on the data module

csvWfExpression.csvexprBody: wt.workflow.engine.WfProcess process = (wt.workflow.engine.WfProcess) self.getObject();@wt.epm.EPMDocument document = (wt.epm.EPMDocument)primaryBusinessObject;@@// Initialize Workflow Variables@String state = document.getState().getState().getDisplay();@com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.log(org.apache.log4j.Level.DEBUG# process# "Workflow started -> " + state);@documentName = document.getName();@@com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.completePreviousProcesses(process);@boolean hasPreviousProcess = com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.hasPreviousProcess(process);@@if(hasPreviousProcess){@ process = com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.setPreviousRoles(process);@ reworkComments = (String)com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.getPreviousProcessVariableValue(process# "reworkComments");@} else {@ process = com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.setProductManagerRoleFromDocumentOrContainer(process);@}@@com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.log(org.apache.log4j.Level.DEBUG# process# "Complete All Previous Processes.");@@wt.part.WTPart[] contentHolders = com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.asps.services.ASPSHelper.getContentHolders(document);@@if(contentHolders.length == 1) {@ contentHolder = contentHolders[0];@} else if(contentHolders.length == 0) {@ com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.log(org.apache.log4j.Level.DEBUG# process# "No Content Holders found for " + documentName);@} else if(contentHolders.length > 1) {@ com.ptc.arbortext.windchill.rules.workflow.WorkflowHelper.log(org.apache.log4j.Level.DEBUG# process# "More than one Content Holder found for " + documentName + "# unable to determine which one is relevant");@}
